  "texts": [
    "However, for our method, we train the model by incorporating all the time series from the dataset together, which provides sufficient pattern diversity.",
    "Furthermore, FCVAE has the ability to extract pattern information due to the addition of frequency information, so it can handle new patterns well.",
    "Nonetheless, even with the introduction of frequency information, anomalies are often challenging to be effectively addressed.",
    "For the model to learn how to handle anomalies, we primarily focus on abnormal data augmentation.",
    "In time series data, anomalies are mostly manifested as pattern mutations or value mutations (shown in Figure 6), (a) Pattern Anomaly (b) Value Anomaly so our data augmentation mainly targets to these two aspects."
  ],
